  - m_Id: 38811963392
    m_Localized: "<color=#610078><align=left><size=60>What is employment in Household
      Service?</color></align></size>\n\nIt is the special employment relationship
      between two people, one being the head of the household who hires, and the
      other being the employee who provides paid services within the family household.\n\n<color=#610078><align=left><size=60>Who
      can employ?</color></align></size>\n\nThe following can employ:\n\n\u25CF The
      person who is the head of the family household or the home where the services
      are provided\n\n\u25CF The owner of the residence when two or more people live
      there without forming a family or a legal entity\n\n<color=#610078><align=left><size=60>Purpose
      of the employment relationship</color></align></size>\n\nPeople working in
      household service can perform the following tasks:\n\n\u25CF Domestic tasks\n\n\u25CF
      Managing and caring for the household as a whole or specific parts of it\n\n\u25CF
      Caring for or attending to family members (children, the elderly, dependents...)\n\n\u25CF
      Other tasks: gardening, house surveillance...\n\n<color=#610078><align=left><size=60>Labor
      reality of domestic workers: challenges and vulnerabilities</color></align></size>\n\nGlobally,
      the majority of domestic workers are women, representing 76.2% of the total,
      although there are also men in this occupation. 81% work in the informal economy,
      with difficult working conditions and low wages. Additionally, they are more
      prone to suffering violence, harassment, and restrictions on their freedom
      of movement.\n\nSOURCES:\n\n<color=blue><u><link=https://tinyurl.com/mumkkt98>https://tinyurl.com/mumkkt98</link>\n\n<link=https://www.nadiesinfuturo.org/IMG/pdf/FOLLETO_SERVICIO_HOGAR_FAMILIAR.pdf>https://www.nadiesinfuturo.org/IMG/pdf/FOLLETO_SERVICIO_HOGAR_FAMILIAR.pdf</link>\n\n<link=https://www.mites.gob.es/es/portada/serviciohogar/preguntas-frecuentes/ambito-aplicacion/index.htm>https://www.mites.gob.es/es/portada/serviciohogar/preguntas-frecuentes/ambito-aplicacion/index.htm</link>\n\n<link=https://www.mites.gob.es/es/portada/serviciohogar/index.htm>https://www.mites.gob.es/es/portada/serviciohogar/index.htm</link></u></color>"
