  - m_Id: 78779486208
    m_Localized: "<color=#610078><align=left><size=60>Regulations</color></align></size>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      Law 27/2011, of August 1, on the update, adequacy, and modernization of the
      Social Security system.\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://tinyurl.com/8fhcbkk6>https://tinyurl.com/8fhcbkk6</link></u></color>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      Royal Decree 1620/2011, of November 14, regulating the special employment relationship
      of household service.\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2011/BOE-A-2011-17975-consolidado.pdf>https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2011/BOE-A-2011-17975-consolidado.pdf</link></u></color>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      Legislative Royal Decree 2/2015, of October 23, Workers' Statute\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2015/BOE-A-2015-11430-consolidado.pdf>https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2015/BOE-A-2015-11430-consolidado.pdf</link></u></color>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      Royal Decree-Law 29/2012, of December 28, on improving management and social
      protection in the Special System for Domestic Employees and other economic
      and social measures.\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://www.boe.es/boe/dias/2012/12/31/pdfs/BOE-A-2012-15764.pdf>https://www.boe.es/boe/dias/2012/12/31/pdfs/BOE-A-2012-15764.pdf</link></u></color>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      Royal Decree-Law 16/2022, of September 6, for the improvement of working conditions
      and Social Security for domestic workers.\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2022/BOE-A-2022-14680-consolidado.pdf>https://www.boe.es/buscar/pdf/2022/BOE-A-2022-14680-consolidado.pdf</link></u></color>\r\n\r\n\u25CF
      IV Provincial Collective Agreement for Home Assistance in Seville\r\n\r\n<color=blue><u><link=https://tinyurl.com/547d4pr2>https://tinyurl.com/547d4pr2</link></u></color>\r"
